      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_5281_zenodo_14822624__task_002/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Here, we introduce the Biosynfoni fingerprint (from BIOSYNFOrmatic fiNgerprInt), which uses 39 structural features aligned with the biosynthetic nature of compounds, moving beyond purely structural characteristics... Biosynfoni is a compact substructure-based molecular fingerprint providing increased interpretability for various natural product cheminformatic applications.",
      "asbval:note": "The research question directly aligns with the paper's core contribution: developing a biosynthesis-informed fingerprint for natural products.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1186-s13321-025-01081-6",
