      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Here, we introduce the Biosynfoni fingerprint (from BIOSYNFOrmatic fiNgerprInt), which uses 39 structural features aligned with the biosynthetic nature of compounds... In total, this added up to 39 substructure keys (Online Figure A26).",
